description: [``botocore``] This release adds new origin timeout options: 1) ResponseCompletionTimeout and 2) OriginReadTimeout (for S3 origins)
[``botocore``] Add support for setting Serverless Scaling Configuration on clusters.

[``botocore``] This release adds support for AWS Managed Microsoft AD Hybrid Edition, introducing new operations: StartADAssessment, DescribeADAssessment, ListADAssessments, DeleteADAssessment, CreateHybridAD, UpdateHybridAD, and DescribeHybridADUpdate; and updated existing operation: DescribeDirectories.
[``botocore``] Release to show the next hop IP address for routes propagated by VPC Route Server into VPC route tables.
[``botocore``] Added TxPowerIndexMin, TxPowerIndexMax, NbTransMin and NbTransMax params to ServiceProfile.
